<title>MY JESUS, I LOVE THEE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal Isu, ka hun hehpih keia Na hi!
 Nang vangin gitloh guolnuom cheng nusieng ka;
 Ka Tanpa lopi ka Hukdampa Na hi,
 Ka Lal Isu, tuhin ka hun hehpih hi!

[V2]
 2. Nei hehpih masak ziekin ka hun hehpih,
 Ngaihdam ka hih nan Kalvari ah Na thii;
 Lung lukhuk Na khuk ziekin ka hun hehpih,
 Ka Lal Isu, tuhin ka hun hehpih hi.

[V3]
 3. Damsung leh thih chan inle hun hehpih ka,
 Hatna nei piek sung chengin hun chawian ka;
 Ka thih ding kuon chan inle ziehih gen ka,
 Ka Lal Isu tuhin kahun hehpih hi.

[V4]
 4. Umna lopi leh nawp tawplohna munah,
 Van In vak achun hun chawian zing ingka;
 Lallukhuk zephawih khu kawmin lasang ka,
 Ka Lal Isu tuhin ka hun hehpih hi.</lyrics>
</song>